data.description: Gorgeous home with all of the amenities and upgrades, offering 5 bedrooms and 2 baths in desirable Oak Forest subdivision. Open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, wood burning fireplace and wet bar. Kitchen is tastefully done w/granite counter tops, custom tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Relax in your large jacuzzi tub with custom tile surround in Master bath. Large covered patio in the backyard, with lots of space to entertain, with privacy fence, shed, rear yard access and a 50' covered carport located on side of the home, for RV or boat parking. New Roof (2022). Security System w/cameras. (2) attic accesses. Never hang Christmas lights again... this home features Trimlight permanent outdoor holiday lighting, customizable, with an easy to use app. X Flood zone. This home has so much to offer and is a must see!!
